MtGox Live is a financial information service that provides a real-time visual display of the buy (bid) and sell (ask) orders currently open on [[MtGox]] exchange along with real time trades and trade history.

This service was first seen in early May, 2011, but first appeared in the forum on May 29, 2011 (1.1).  It first appeared under the name, *mtgoxlive.bco.in* but later changed it's name to *mtgoxlive.com*.

The page requires a browser that supports Websockets (1.2).  Apple Safari (1.3) and Google Chrome (1.4) are two such browsers that support Websockets. 

